3:
"I have declared the things from long ago; they came out from my mouth, and I made them known;
\q1 then suddenly I did them, and they came to pass.
\q1

21:
They did not thirst when he led them through the deserts;
\q1 he made the water to flow out of the rock for them;
\q1 he split open the rock, and the waters gushed out.
\q1
